(firstQuint)Ribavirin, Its Dosing Regime.

 The standard treatment of patients with chronic hepatitis C infection (HCV) is treatment with ribavirin.

 Actually, the compliance (2x daily) seems to be a problem.

 To increase patients' compliance, it is investigated if the total dose of ribavirin can be taken once daily.

 The pharmacokinetics of ribavirin at different dosage regimes is investigated.

